      <p>A game where the player will get six anonymous contestants as potential love interests. <br> They will be hidden to the player until the end of the game. The contests are asked a list of questions, <br> and the player will pick whose answer they like best. At the end the answers are tallied up and the <br> most chosen contestant is the one for the player.</p>

      <img src="game.jpg" alt="Code" width="300" height="200">
      
