      <img id="bottomImage" src="code2.png" alt="Code" width="300" height="200">

      <li> The calculate personality result function calculates the result by taking each picked answer <br>
	and storing the choice in a variable. It then sorts through the chosen answers to figure out which had <br>
	the highest chosen frequency</li>
